content:
for the second account , teams you can make : 
1. Mouchette Aigis Faint Thais. Can replace Faint for Helot once you get her AND if you need more damage. Faint if having issues with survivability.
2. Caecus-Goliath-Salvador-Thais. Classic counter team with Caecus as carry. You dupe caecus 2 cost via Thais exalt to stack counter ideally with Goliath temp str exalt. Salvador is there for furnace and fat shields and also situational crit on his exalt. All of them have good Con Stats so they're gonna be beefy.
